<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道<delay8 />
<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />那裡可以體驗<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />ＤＩＹ<colour id="65535" />活動嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也用島上收集到的材料<delay20 />
自己做了道具<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我技術不好，還做得很爛，<delay8 />
但能使用自己做出來的道具，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的會覺得非常感動喔──！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且體驗活動是免費的，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />學會<colour id="1" />ＤＩＹ<colour id="65535" />之後，在生活上也很方便，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我推薦你一定要去參加看看──！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當初想說反正這裡是無人島，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以就身無分文地搬過來了。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />還好那時候去了<colour id="3" />豆狸<colour id="65535" />那裡，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他願意收購我帶去的各種東西，幫了不少忙！<10_4 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說來說去，金錢果然還是不可或缺的啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之，我打算暫時在島上<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />賣些自己捕獲的東西，或是幫忙除除草，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一點一點地慢慢存錢啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說只要是廣場以外的地方，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管你想要放置私人物品，<delay8 />
還是裝飾這座島都是自由的喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以後有機會的話，<delay8 />
我也好想在外面擺健身用品，<delay20 />
打造一個戶外健身房啊──！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<tag a="110" b="1" />有什麼<delay8 />
能讓島上熱鬧起來的好點子，<delay20 />
就按照自己的想法去做吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了！我曾經聽<colour id="3" />豆狸<colour id="65535" />說過，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他那裡似乎有賣一些<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生活上的必需品喔？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算是在無人島上生活，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但因為有移居套餐計劃，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以還是能得到不少各方面的幫助！<pageBreak /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過因為我沒帶錢就搬來這裡了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以目前比起去買東西，<delay8 />
我更常去找他賣東西就是了──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
